.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, pumpkin, strawberry, pineapple
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, satire, spy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, indie, r&b
House: cottage, colonial, tower, craftsman
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, handball, parkour, skiing
 1. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 2. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the craftsman house##1
 4. the person eating pineapple is on the far right##1
 5. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 7. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 8. the colonial house is the fan of r&b##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is the fan of indie##1
10. the fan of disco is on the far right##1
11. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Food      | pumpkin      | raspberry     | strawberry    | pineapple |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | drama   | satire   | spy           |
| Music-Genre   | electronic  | r&b     | indie    | disco         |
| House           | craftsman         | colonial | tower     | cottage        |
| Sport         | cricket     | skiing  | handball | parkour       |

