.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, cauliflower, grapes, lettuce
There are 4 different nationalities: american, british, chinese, french
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, mouse, rabbit
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, siglo, game, old-henry
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, fuchsia, orange, blue
 1. the dunhill-smoker is on the far left##1
 2. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
 3. the person eating grapes is the owner of the rabbit##1
 4. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
 5. the game-smoker is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 6. the person who likes blue is the person eating grapes##1
 7. the chinese is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 8. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
 9. the french is the owner of the frog##1
10. the british is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
11. the person who likes blue is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
12. the person eating grapes is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Food          | cabbage    | lettuce      | grapes  | cauliflower   |
| Nationality   | french     | chinese      | british | american      |
| Pet           | frog       | fish         | rabbit  | mouse         |
| Cigar         | dunhill | siglo | game  | old-henry |
| Color     | orange       | lavender         | blue   | fuchsia        |

