4 different pets are kept: cat, goat, guinea-pig, snake
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, roller, taxi, trike
 1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 2. the security-guard is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 3. the person driving the roller is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 7. the thai is on the far right##1
 8. the security-guard is on the right of the japanese##1
 9. the indonesian is on the left of the pilot##1
10. the person who growslily is on the far right##1
11. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left##1
12. the person driving the trike is on the left of the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Flower      | daisy   | amaryllis   | orchid      | lily     |
| Job          | musician     | pilot   | security-guard | lawyer |
| Nationality   | indonesian | japanese | chinese   | thai       |
