11. the colonial house is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
12. the journalist is on the far left##1
13. the colonial house is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
14. the modern house is on the right of the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |    4     |
