 2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
 4. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 5. the person playing scrabble is the fan of rock##1
 6. the fan of metal is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person playing poker##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
10. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
11. the person who's birthday is in december is the person playing scrabble##1
12. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
