10. the person who's sport is soccer is the owner of the dog##1
11. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
12. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Sport    | baseball     | cycling  | soccer       | skateboarding      |
| Hobby       | singing    | writing        | collecting  | drawing      |
| Job         | fisherman  | security-guard | firefighter | photographer |
| Pet         | chinchilla | mouse          | dog         | hamster      |
| Game   | billiard     | go     | scrabble       | snooker          |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, august, december, february
House: palace, townhouse, victorian, tower
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller, western
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, british, indonesian, mexican
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, rat, snake
 1. the indonesian is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is the person watching western movies##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 4. the mexican is on the left of the brazilian##1
 5. the victorian house is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 6. the tower house is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the townhouse house is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 8. the brazilian is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is the person watching thriller movies##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
11. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
12. the tower house is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Birthday      | february       | december      | august      | may    |
| House         | tower | victorian | townhouse | palace  |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller    | mystery     | western      | disaster |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | mexican     | brazilian    | british  |
| Pet           | chinchilla  | snake       | cat          | rat      |

