.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, cola, juice
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, rock-climbing, singing, video-games
4 different games are played: domino, snooker, whist, canasta
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, rowing, skiing
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, motorbike, ship
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 3. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 4. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 5. the person playing domino is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 6. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is the person drinking cola##1
11. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
13. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage          | juice      | milk     | iced-tea        | cola     |
| Hobby         | singing     | chess    | video-games | rock-climbing |
| Game   | domino | whist  | snooker      | canasta       |
| Sport         | rowing      | lacrosse | parkour     | skiing        |
| Transport     | motorbike   | ship     | helicopter  | jet-ski       |

